lead_paragraph: After the Washington Wizards lost for the fifth time in six games under new coach Scott Brooks, shooting guard Bradley Beal stood in the home locker room and spoke in hushed tones, trying to wrap his head around what's gone wrong so far.

headline.print_headline: Thanks in Part to Defensive Chaos, 1-5 Wizards 'Frustrated'
